{"id": "24701", "post": "<div class=\"post-24701 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-poll tag-pollresults\" id=\"post-24701\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-results-how-many-offers-should-we-publish-per-month/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Poll Results: How many offers should we publish per month?</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/poll/\" rel=\"tag\">poll</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/pollresults/\" rel=\"tag\">pollresults</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> September 4, 2020 @ 7:27 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMjQ1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDE2IDI0NSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lowendbox-poll-results.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"245\"></a></p><p>On August 23rd, we asked you to tell us <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-how-many-offers-should-we-publish-per-month/\">how many offers we should publish per month</a>.&nbsp; After 12 days of voting and 163 votes, the results are in:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MDEiIGhlaWdodD0iMjk3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTAxIDI5NyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-24702\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-04-at-15.59.53.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"297\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-04-at-15.59.53.png.webp 884w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-04-at-15.59.53-300x178.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-04-at-15.59.53-768x455.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 501px) 100vw, 501px\"></p><p>In other words, you want more offers, more options, and as many choices as possible \u2013 not surprising for a consumer looking for deals in the marketplace!</p><p>LowEndBox is constantly on the lookout for deals and we source offers from multiple sources:</p><ul><li>Many hosts contact us and <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/submit-an-offer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">submit offers</a>.&nbsp; It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for them to get free advertising exposure, connect with our audience, and build organic search traffic.</li><li>We watch our sister site, <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com\">LowEndTalk</a>, and contact hosts who post there, asking if they\u2019d like to mirror their offers on LEB.</li><li>When our staff comes across an interesting offer on another site, we sometimes drop them a line, asking them if they\u2019d like to post on LEB.</li></ul><p>Our goal is to get as many fresh offers in front of our readers as possible.</p><p>We also invite users to <a href=\"https://lowendbox.freshdesk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">contact us</a> if they come across interesting deals in their Internet travels.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDAwIDIwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone siz